    m_Localized: <link=ContactSupport>Contact Support</link>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25194466137165824
    m_Localized: Do you want to delete your account?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25194466179108864
    m_Localized: If you continue, you will be able to delete your account, after
      that you will not be able to access any Energy 8 products under this account.
      After deletion, you will be able to contact support for data recovery within
      two weeks, after this period your account will be permanently deleted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
